<P>
   TOUR-DE-FRANCE (Cap d'Gde, France) _ The Tour de France is
unraveling in full view as three banned Festina riderr admit that
</P>
<P>
   they took performance)enhancing drugs, including the drug EPO.
Meanwhile, riders from a Dutch team are being questioned following
the discovery of drug paraphernalia and masking agen|s in their
hotel, and angry riders delay the start of Friday's stage. By
Samuel Abt.
</P>
<P>
   With
