   EOS-MUSIC-REVIEW (New York) _ Lincoln Center Festival: EOS
Orchestra, ``Literally: Bernstein'': Jonathan Sheffer, conductor;
at Alice Tully Hall. Reviewed by James R. Oestreich.
</P>
