<P>
   WARSH-COLUMN (Undated) _ Remember ``Yellow Rain?'' The 1980s
equivalent of CNN's ``nerve gas'' fiasco is interesting for the
light is casts on the economic and political landcape of the
present day. By David Warsh. 1700 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
