<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-24 16:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1579 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOUSTON-HEAT-HNS &LR;      07-24 1134
