<HEADLINE>
(EMBARGOED FOR RELEASE SUNDAY, JULY 26)  
 DOG-CAT LIST 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By RICHARD NILSEN  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   UNDATED - Who is a dog and who is a cat? The list is clear. &QL; 
