</P>
<P>
   AT&AMP;T-EXPAND (Undated) _ Expansion plans of AT&AMP;T Corp. By Seth
Schiesel.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   (Display)
</P>
<P>
   TVDINNER-TRANSFORM (Cherry Hill, N.J.) _ Vlasic, which was spun
off from Campbell Soup a year ago, is trying to revitalize a group
of food businesses that its old parent company decided it did not
need. Some analysts think the effort could produce healthy profits.
By Constance L. Hays.
</P>
<P>
   (Previously slugged VLASIC)
</P>
<P>
