   SNAKE-AWOL _ Alissss is missing again. Nearly a year after the
boa escaped from a Los Angeles home and ate a Chihuahua, the
reptile has disappeared again. Exiled to Birmingham, Ala., after
Los Angeles animal officials spent six months deciding if Alissss's
owner, rock musician Angus Johnson, should receive a snake permit,
the snake was either stolen or has once again escaped. He's been
AWOL since Saturday. Amy Collins. (Will move in the ``a'' national
