given the boy just a short time to live, but his father wouldn't
give up. He searched the Internet, coming upon a woman who helped
the couple and their son come to the United States where UCLA
doctors have saved the child's life. By Yvette Cabrera. (Will move
in the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news files.)
