<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-24 20:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2100 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BIZWEEK-$ADV26-ART-NY     07-24 1301
